                <h1 class="main-title"><i data-lucide="puzzle"></i>発達障害・情緒障害の理解と支援</h1>
            </div>

            <div class="note-container">
                <div class="note-header">
                    <div class="note-title"><i data-lucide="book-open-check"></i>暗記ノート</div>
